lead_paragraph: He doesn't flash that easygoing smile as frequently. His play gets scrutinized and picked apart more, because many of the folks who gushed about Deshaun Watson's game a season ago now focus on the overthrows and critical interceptions.

headline.print_headline: Watson's Trip to Heisman Trophy Stage Bumpier Than 2015
